Package: ar0822-rpi-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, dkms
Recommends: linux-headers-rpi-2712 | linux-headers-rpi-v8
Description: Onsemi AR0822 camera driver for Raspberry Pi (DKMS)
 Kernel module and device tree overlay for Onsemi AR0822, an 8 MP
 rolling shutter CMOS sensor, on Raspberry Pi with kernel 6.12 or newer.
 .
 DKMS builds the module on target, so one package covers every Raspberry Pi
 OS release and kernel update. Installing it also places ar0822 overlay
 in /boot/overlays.
